Wed Feb 25 22:28:07 UTC 2026 - Aaron Puchert <aaronpuchert@alice-dsl.net>

- Initial (separate) release based on version 9.1.0.
  * Changed the requirement prefix of the standard library from Coq
    to Stdlib and made it mandatory. As a temporary measure, for
    backward compatibility with older versions, Coq, or a missing
    From Stdlib, is translated to Stdlib with a warning.
  * Detailed change logs are available under
    https://rocq-prover.org/doc/v9.0/refman-stdlib/changes.html
    and https://rocq-prover.org/doc/v9.1/refman-stdlib/changes.html.
